::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer glances at the hand, his mind working over what the femm had just 
said. Research? That could be usefull for the Alliance

"Wait just a moment here!" he says, his tone suddenly twice as friendly, "I 
didn't mean to lead you out just yet! We might be able to use ya, after all! 
What kind of research do you do? Weapons and such?"
